## Gateway ACL Security System

A strict 3-layer access control system that intercepts **every** HTTP request before it reaches any endpoint handler.

### Architecture

```
Incoming Request
       |
       v
+---------------------+
|  Security Middleware |  <-- Intercepts ALL requests
|  (FastAPI layer)     |
+---------------------+
       |
       v
+---------------------+
|    ACL Engine        |  <-- 3-layer evaluation
|  1. IP Layer         |  Whitelist/blacklist by CIDR
|  2. Session Layer    |  JWT phase validation
|  3. Device Layer     |  Per-device endpoints + rate limit
+---------------------+
       |
  ALLOW / DENY(403)
       |
       v
  Endpoint Handler
```

### Three ACL Layers

| Layer | What it checks | Deny reason |
|-------|---------------|-------------|
| **IP** | Source IP against whitelist/blacklist (CIDR) | `IP_BLACKLISTED`, `IP_NOT_WHITELISTED` |
| **Session** | JWT presence, validity, phase (`phase1`/`phase2`/`device_auth`) | `SESSION_MISSING`, `SESSION_INVALID`, `SESSION_PHASE_INSUFFICIENT` |
| **Device** | Device registration, block status, endpoint permissions, rate limit | `DEVICE_BLOCKED`, `DEVICE_ENDPOINT_DENIED`, `DEVICE_RATE_LIMITED` |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Blacklist overrides whitelist.** A blacklisted IP is denied even if it's within the VPN subnet.
> All denied requests are logged to both in-memory storage and persistent file at `logs/acl_blocked.log`.

### Route Classification

| Category | Routes | Auth Required |
|----------|--------|--------------|
| **Public** | `/health`, `/docs`, `/openapi.json`, `/redoc` | None |
| **Unauthenticated** | `/register`, `/login`, `/device/register`, `/device/auth` | None |
| **Phase 1** | `/verify-otp` | Phase1 token |
| **Device** | `/device/telemetry` | Device token |
| **Protected** | Everything else (`/me`, `/vpn/*`, `/gateway/*`) | Phase2 (full 2FA) |

### Admin Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Purpose |
|--------|----------|---------|
| `GET` | `/gateway/acl/stats` | Enforcement statistics (evaluations, denials by layer) |
| `GET` | `/gateway/acl/blocked` | View recent blocked request log |
| `POST` | `/gateway/acl/blacklist` | Blacklist an IP/CIDR range |
| `DELETE` | `/gateway/acl/blacklist` | Remove IP from blacklist |
| `POST` | `/gateway/acl/block-device` | Block a device by ID |
| `POST` | `/gateway/acl/unblock-device` | Unblock a device |

